```bash
uvx pre-commit run --all-files
```

The base layer contributes universal hygiene + language-agnostic governance enforcement; the
python stack overlay adds ruff / ruff-format / pyright (strict) / the structure-lint
(`tests/test_structure.py`) / pytest. Run the same gate locally that CI runs.

